OL,3,CGrandad and granddaughter thank
OL,4,Clifeboat crew who rescued them off
OL,5,CSussex coast
OL,7,FA grandad and his granddaughter have
OL,8,Fthanked the lifeboat crew who rescued
OL,9,Fthem off the Sussex coast.
OL,11,FSteve Close, 61, was in a kayak while
OL,12,FAlyssa, 11, was on a paddleboard off
OL,13,FPevensey when the weather worsened,
OL,14,Fblowing them almost two miles out to
OL,15,Fsea.
OL,17,FAlyssa lost her paddle and they knew
OL,18,Fthey were in trouble. Fortunately,
OL,19,Fthey were well prepared, wearing
OL,20,Fwetsuits, buoyancy aids and carrying a
OL,21,Fmobile phone in a waterproof pouch.
