OL,7,FBack at the beach, Steve's wife Sharon
OL,8,Fwas watching them with growing concern
OL,9,Fwhen she got a call from Steve.
OL,11,FSteve said: "I phoned Sharon to ask
OL,12,Ffor help and she called 999 for the
OL,13,FCoastguard. We keptdrifting, so I got
OL,14,FAlyssa into the kayak and we lashed it
OL,15,Ftogether with the paddleboard."
