OL,4,Clifeboat crew who rescued them off
OL,5,CSussex coast
OL,7,FSteve and Alyssa were quickly drifting
OL,8,Fout of sight but Eastbourne RNLI's
OL,9,Finshore lifeboat was soon on scene and
OL,10,Fbrought them both back to shore, where
OL,11,Fthey were met by the Eastbourne
OL,12,FCoastguard Rescue Team.
OL,14,FSteve added: "We did the right thing.
OL,15,FEveryone knew where we were, and
OL,16,Fsomeone was on the beach able to keep
OL,17,Fa lookout.
