OL,3,CGrandad and granddaughter thank
OL,4,Clifeboat crew who rescued them off
OL,5,CSussex coast
OL,7,F"I was used to the currents but the
OL,8,Fwind just overtook us. Once we were
OL,9,Fbeyond the sandbar we were in deeper
OL,10,Fwater and we dared not get out."
OL,12,FOn Monday (12 August), the pair
OL,13,Freunited with the crew that saved them
OL,14,Fto thank them and warn others.
OL,16,FLast year, paddleboard rescues tripled
OL,17,Ffrom 52 in 2019 to 155 in 2023.
