OL,3,CGrandad and granddaughter thank
OL,4,Clifeboat crew who rescued them off
OL,5,CSussex coast
OL,7,F"Our rescue data shows that almost
OL,8,Fhalf of lifeboat launches to
OL,9,Fpaddleboarders were due to offshore
OL,10,Fwinds and tides, something water users
OL,11,Fcan check before hitting the water.
OL,13,F"If you are on a lifeguarded beach,
OL,14,Fkeep an eye out for the orange
OL,15,Fwindsock to see which way the wind is
OL,16,Fblowing."
